@baseUrl = http://localhost:5274

### Get alle workouts (gesorteerd op datum)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workouts

### Get workout by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workouts/1

### Create nieuwe workout - Bench Press 80kg (eerste keer = automatisch PR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workouts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Bench Press",
    "reps": 8,
    "weight": 80
}

### Create nieuwe workout - Bench Press 85kg (hoger = automatisch PR!)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workouts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Bench Press",
    "reps": 8,
    "weight": 85
}

### Create nieuwe workout - Bench Press 82kg (lager = geen PR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workouts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Bench Press",
    "reps": 10,
    "weight": 82
}

### Create nieuwe workout - Deadlift
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workouts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Deadlift",
    "reps": 5,
    "weight": 140
}

### Create nieuwe workout - Squat
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workouts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Squat",
